libxnvctrl: libxnvctrl (Library providing the NV-CONTROL API)
libxnvctrl:
libxnvctrl: This packages contains the libXNVCtrl library from the nvidia-settings
libxnvctrl: application. This library provides the NV-CONTROL API for
libxnvctrl: communicating with the proprietary NVidia xorg driver. This package
libxnvctrl: does not contain the nvidia-settings tool itself as that is included
libxnvctrl: with the proprietary drivers themselves. 
libxnvctrl:
libxnvctrl: ftp://download.nvidia.com/XFree86/nvidia-settings/
